Dr. Birkin.

263
00:22:27,463 --> 00:22:30,258
Psychologist? Why? Was she hysterical?

264
00:22:30,341 --> 00:22:33,511
No. No. On the contrary.

265
00:22:33,595 --> 00:22:35,972
