393
00:30:40,956 --> 00:30:43,501
There's Grandpa Barton.

394
00:30:43,584 --> 00:30:45,127
Barton.

395
00:30:45,961 --> 00:30:47,797
Oh, hello, Frank. How you doing?

396
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:49,382
