it's going to work out.

407
00:31:15,282 --> 00:31:18,369
- What hotel are you staying in?
- Park Plaza.

408
00:31:18,452 --> 00:31:22,957
You know, I was even thinking about
going out to that old house again.

409
00:31:23,040 --> 00:31:26,502
